      "acceptanceCriteria": "Ansys Mechanical commercial solver with documented V&V; FDA in-house code with unit test suite; version control and audit trail for all analysis scripts.",
      "rationale": "All three FEA environments (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) operate under documented SQA programs. Commercial solver release notes and regression test results are on file. In-house scripts are version-controlled in Git with peer review records. Achieves Gradation 2."
