      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent review of model setup, boundary conditions, and material assignments by a second analyst not involved in original model construction.",
      "rationale": "A second analyst independently reviewed boundary conditions, contact definitions, material assignments, and load application against the ASTM F1717 protocol. No discrepancies were identified. Gradation 2 achieved."
    },
    {
