      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties (E, yield stress, tangent modulus) sourced from coupon tests of same material lot; geometric dimensions from CMM measurements of test specimens.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus (114 GPa), yield stress (880 MPa), and tangent modulus (2.2 GPa) for Ti-6Al-4V were measured from the same material lot as test specimens. Screw and rod dimensions verified by CMM. Input uncertainty quantified and propagated. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
