      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were tested across two independent laboratories. All specimens sourced from production lots with full material traceability. CMM inspection confirmed dimensional conformance. Gradation 3 achieved."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Multiple load levels or construct configurations tested; environmental conditions (temperature, humidity) monitored and reported.",
      "rationale": "Testing was performed under a single ASTM F1717 configuration (compression-bending at ambient temperature). Only one load condition was evaluated, limiting the ability to characterize model behavior across the full operating range. Environmental conditions were monitored but not varied. Achieves Gradation 2 only; below required Gradation 3. This is the one factor below required level."
    },
    {
