      "rationale": "FEA model geometry was parameterized from CMM measurements of each test specimen individually. Material properties matched to coupon tests from the same lot. Boundary conditions replicate the ASTM F1717 fixture geometry and loading axis. Equivalency documented in analysis plan. Gradation 3 achieved."
