      "rationale": "The validation metric E/uval was computed for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement across all 11 specimens. Maximum E/uval was 1.44 (force at 40 mm); all QoIs within 10% relative error. Pre-specified acceptance criteria met. Gradation 3 achieved."
