      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three QoIs specified in the FDA guidance for pedicle screw mechanical testing submissions. These directly reflect clinical failure modes (fatigue initiation at yield, catastrophic fracture). Gradation 3 achieved."
