      "rationale": "The validation activity is the COU itself: the FEA model is validated against the same ASTM F1717 compression-bending protocol that constitutes the regulatory submission test. No domain extrapolation is required. The validation scenario, specimen geometry, loading, and QoIs are identical to the intended use. Gradation 3 achieved."
